lines.text: Gravity and other effects show its presence
What makes up dark matter is a matter of speculation
Universe started as dense and hot
Scientist have discovered multiple forms of evidence of Big Bang

secText:
Lesson:
1. Define the [OBJ:expsec_A419:Standard Model].
2. Identify the [OBJ:expsec_A420:quarks and leptons] in the Standard Model.
3. Identify the [OBJ:expsec_A421:forces] in the Standard Model.
4. Describe the [OBJ:expsec_A422:Higgs boson].
5. Define [OBJ:expsec_A423:dark matter].
6. Define [OBJ:expsec_A423mi:dark energy].
7. Describe [OBJ:expsec_A424:black holes].
8. Analyze [OBJ:expsec_A425:gravitational lensing].
9. Describe the [OBJ:expsec_A426:Big Bang].
